    private static class HFilePrettyPrinter.SimpleReporter
extends com.codahale.metrics.ScheduledReporter
    Almost identical to ConsoleReporter, but extending ScheduledReporter, as extending ConsoleReporter in this version of dropwizard is now too much trouble.
